          # Local AI Chatbot

A fully offline, rule-based chatbot written in pure Python. No API keys, no internet connection, no paid services required.

## How it works

The bot matches your input against known intents (`chatbot/intents.json`) using a blend of sequence similarity and token-overlap scoring, falling back to a generic response if nothing matches well enough.

